{"type":null,"faqId":10160,"title":"G6-U00网络流量节省小窍门","answer":"&nbsp;\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>（1）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">不使用数据业务时，关闭数据业务功能。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>（2）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">有<span>WLAN</span>环境时，使用<span>WLAN</span>网络，关闭数据业务。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>（3）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">登录<span>wap</span>网站比登录<span>www</span>网站更节省流量。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>（4）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">关闭数据业务：在主屏幕，点击<b>设置</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>全部</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>移动网络</b>，关闭<b>始终连接数据业务</b>开关。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';font-size:10.5pt;\">关闭后台数据同步：在主屏幕，点击<b>设置</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>全部</b><span>-&gt;</span><b>帐户</b>，关闭帐户与同步。</span>","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"738","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396603821000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":4,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"网络流量节省小窍门","avgScore":0.0,"c